{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came to raid, and raid, and grabbed them to-- to concentration camps, or who knows.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody ever knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They never know where to turn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the fear, the terror, was always with us constantly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a horrifying-- horrifying feeling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one night, Daddy was that time already, I think, he was that time in Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was with Mom, and we were upstairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We head from our kitchen upstairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had stairs to go up to our master bedroom, to Daddy's bedroom.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Mom was shaking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was trembling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She could see the Germans at night with the German shepherds, walking around, snooping around, see what they can find.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Jews, some were hiding in the backyard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I-- we were trembling because we thought every minute they might come in to us, but somehow our thing was confusing, because we had the front door locked up, camouflaging like supposedly we are out of, and nobody's there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had this, and the other family was living there, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a confusion, so I went through with that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then Daddy, all of a sudden when he went down, they told, if you don't have a certain card, when he's gonna work for the Germans, he would remain home.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he did joined us in town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One day the whole streetcar was surrounded, and he was sent to concentration camp, to Ottmuth Later on he was sent to Markstadt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now to me, and then everybody was afraid the-- the children they also not safe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So my daddy, my mom, the cousins, they had connection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had-- they found out all kind of secrets, which they informed us.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
